the 825 GB number is actually because the motherboard has 3 small 275 GB SSDs on it. If you subtract the OS from the PS5 storage it actually comes out to about 650-700 GB of storage.  Also, the 8k advertised on the PS5 box is only for movies to my knowledge, games will cap out at 4k (the xbox actually has higher performance)
